OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy,
OL,6,Fwet evening with occasionally heavy
OL,7,Frain spreading eastwards. Turning
OL,8,Fdrier through the rest of the night
OL,9,Fwith some clearer spells developing.
OL,10,FBlustery winds, strong at times.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FA bright, breezy and largely
OL,13,Fdry day, with sunny spells and just
OL,14,Fthe slight chance of an isolated light
OL,15,Fshower in the west.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FA
OL,18,Fchangeable, often cloudy and breezy
OL,19,Ffew days with spells of rain, but some
OL,20,Fdrier and brighter periods too.
